('3351', '2', 'To prepare relish, coat bell pepper pieces with cooking spray.'),
('3351', '3', 'Place pepper pieces on grill rack. grill 3 minutes on each side or until lightly charred.'),
('3351', '4', 'Remove from grill. cool slightly. Coarsely chop bell pepper pieces.'),
('3351', '5', 'Combine chopped bell peppers, parsley, and next 6 ingredients. set aside.'),
('3351', '6', 'To prepare fish, brush 1 tablespoon oil evenly over fish. Sprinkle fish evenly with thyme, 3/4 teaspoon salt, and 1/2 teaspoon black pepper.'),
('3351', '7', 'Place fish on grill rack. grill 4 minutes on each side or until desired degree of doneness.'),
('3351', '8', 'Serve with relish.'),
('3352', '1', 'Finely grate 1 teaspoon zest from a grapefruit. Squeeze 1/2 cup juice from a white grapefruit.'),
('3352', '2', 'Cut peel, including all white pith, from remaining fruit with a sharp paring knife and cut segments free from membranes. Chop enough grapefruit segments (use all colors) to measure 1/2 cup. Reserve 1 cup of remaining whole segments.'),
('3352', '3', 'Boil juice, wine, shallot, and vinegar in a small heavy saucepan until reduced to about 1 tablespoon. Reduce heat to low and whisk in butter 1 piece at a time, lifting pan from heat occasionally to cool sauce and adding each new piece of butter before previous one has melted completely (sauce must not get hot enough to separate).'),
('3352', '4', 'Stir in chopped grapefruit and season with salt and pepper. Keep beurre blanc warm in a metal bowl set over a saucepan of hot water.'),
('3353', '1', 'Prepare barbecue (medium-high heat). Thread jalapeno and garlic clove onto metal skewer.'),
('3353', '2', 'Brush jalapeno, garlic, fish, and red bell peppers with oil. sprinkle with salt and pepper. Sprinkle fish with 1/2 teaspoon cumin and 1/2 teaspoon coriander. Grill fish, bell peppers,jalapeno, and garlic until vegetables are tender and charred and fish is just cooked through, about 4 minutes per side for fish and 8 minutes per side for vegetables. Grill lemon, cut side down, until charred, about 3 minutes.'),
('3353', '3', 'Transfer fish to plate and tent with foil to keep warm.'),
('3353', '4', 'Peel charred parts of skin from bell peppers and cut stem from jalapeno, and transfer to blender, discarding peel and stem.'),
('3353', '5', 'Add garlic clove, remaining 1/4 cup oil, 1 1/2 teaspoons cumin, and 1 1/2 teaspoons coriander to blender. Process until coarse puree forms. Season sauce generously to taste with salt and pepper.'),
('3353', '6', 'Place 1 fish fillet on each of 4 plates. Squeeze grilled lemon over. Spoon sauce over fish and serve.'),
